      <br />
      <p>
        The top 5 teams should submit a technical report of 2-6 pages inclusive of any references, detailing their
        solution to the OpenReview challenge venue (TBD). Authors are required to include a 
        <span class="font-bold">"Social Impacts Statement"</span>
        that highlights potential broader impact of their work, including its ethical aspects and future societal
